metadata.name: ChocoMaoNFT #2
metadata.description: 1555 Choco Maos that will symbolize the history of Mao an abandoned cat, finds shelter at a chocolate shop owned by a kind old man. There, he discovers his passion for experimenting with different ingredients and creates his own recipe, which proves to be a great success under the name Choco Mao when the old man starts selling it. Mao becomes the official mascot of the chocolate and enjoys his new life at the chocolate shop.
